{"tid":1569831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足，記得做任務呀！","createTime":"2019-09-14T18:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T18:46:40.000Z","uid":13586,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35321f176b1e16b415b4a1abb317cc154f9a6ef7","tid":1569831,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:18:27.000Z","msg":"有人覺得而家係中盤，半場，樽頸，甚至步雨運後塵，運動收皮中<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但記住兩樣：</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 冇得再輸，輸咗港共中共任佢玩死香港<br />\n2. 發夢，設死線，升級，無限loop </span><br />\n<br />\n所以記得做任務呀<br />\n<strong>日任：</strong><br />\n整連儂牆<br />\n係要非一般連儂牆，唔係俾我地睇<br />\n係俾非同温層同淺藍睇，所以長輩牆也毋妨<br />\n<br />\n<strong>文宣</strong><br />\n唔識photoshop唔緊要，但一定要send 行出嚟<br />\n特別係行動post一定要推上熱門<br />\n仲有國際戰線，無論白宮聯署，Twitter同Reddit好需要大家<br />\n200萬人一人一upvote 其實唔難<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唱歌，叫口號，人鏈</strong><br />\n好支持，但唔好多，多會膠化<br />\n可以士氣buff，記住最尾要嗌完發夢日，邊度見<br />\n<br />\n<strong>週任：</strong><br />\n發夢<br />\n記得自己崗位<br />\n和理非唔大好做散水撚<br />\n前線勇武唔好屌自己人同手足<br />\n但無論點，核爆都唔割<br />\n仲有唔好淨係run，係<strong>hit and run</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>突發任：</strong><br />\n好似721咁，個個仲係睇緊潑黑中聯辦嗰時元朗恐襲<br />\n我相信大家冇gear都有手機掛<br />\n記得錄起佢，唔止影相，要錄，人人都係記者<br />\n有gear更加要幫手<br />\n<br />\n見嗰日做哂任嘅，冇嘢做條條fing ：<br />\n做吓gym，要大隻過啲黑警<br />\n熟讀被捕需知，俾人拉都知點算<br />\n睇藍屍共狗黑警而家戰術，知己知彼<br />\n<br />\n我地已經冇嘢好輸，輸埋嘅真心個個因為香港冇希望而移民同自殺都唔出奇，所以就算final bos係中共都要贏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>[gold]光復香港    時代革命gold]</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSEnnVg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSEnnVg.jpg&h=48f97423&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i85t2Vh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi85t2Vh.png&h=fbe3437f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7ennVh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7ennVh.jpg&h=d9d27a65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfce2579eb109d4c16ef3f4a882a811928aaeee8","tid":1569831,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0521a1104d59c775ddd515486db8778e02509d56","tid":1569831,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc4fab93637ee287503917b7d062a45aa8667a98","tid":1569831,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:23:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f19733de123764bb3c73354648645c6327d7269d","tid":1569831,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=cc18f71f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=f9a7dfd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"017015a6cc5afb280073ef5a46fa3660c053eb13","tid":1569831,"uid":84632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:24:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1adf89ba15f6b1998b7d10417d3b4587733fc0a","tid":1569831,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:26:16.000Z","msg":"鐘仲眼瞓咁打，狂打錯字"},{"pid":"f4455c8c0c42deb986af7ab997c2e2bd13bfdd45","tid":1569831,"uid":81702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53157f4c0cffb8b87f458078f940e72dc83e86b2","tid":1569831,"uid":322373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:46:40.000Z","msg":"好奇一問：仲可以點升級？由邊個做？有無共識？有咩可以要脅政府？"}]}